# RajMarg Elite — Complete Project Overview

## What Is This Project?

**RajMarg Elite** is a **premium taxi booking web application** for **Gujarat, India**. It allows customers to book intercity taxi rides between major Gujarat cities (and Mumbai), choose from multiple car categories and driver tiers, calculate fares, make simulated payments, and track their rides — all within a polished, premium-looking single-page app.

> **Tagline:** *"Gujarat's Premium Taxi Service — Book. Ride. Repeat."*

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Version |
|---|---|---|
| **Framework** | React | 19.1 |
| **Build Tool** | Vite | 6.3 |
| **Routing** | React Router DOM | 7.13 |
| **State Management** | Redux Toolkit | 2.11 |
| **Animations** | Framer Motion | 12.34 |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | 4.2 (via `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin) |
| **PWA Support** | vite-plugin-pwa | 1.2 |
| **Fonts** | Google Fonts (Playfair Display, Inter, DM Sans) | — |

### Not Using (No Backend)
- No backend server / API
- No real database — **localStorage** is used for all persistence
- No real payment gateway — uses a **fake Razorpay modal**
- No real authentication — uses **hardcoded demo accounts**
- No real maps/GPS — uses a **static distance matrix**

---

