## Pages & Features

### 1. Home Page (`/`)
The landing page with 7 sections:
- **HeroBooking**: Full-screen hero with background gradient, tagline, and an inline quick-booking form (from/to city, trip type)
- **WhyChooseUs**: Feature highlights (GPS tracking, verified drivers, 24/7 support, etc.)
- **CarCategories**: Showcase of 5 car types (Mini, Sedan, SUV, Premium SUV, Luxury)
- **HowItWorks**: 3-step process (Book → Pay → Ride)
- **RouteCoverage**: Display of covered Gujarat routes
- **Testimonials**: Customer review cards
- **MobileAppPromo**: App download CTA section

### 2. Booking Page (`/booking`)
A **multi-step booking wizard** (BookingWizard component):
- **Step 1**: Select pickup city & drop-off city (22 Gujarat cities supported)
- **Step 2**: Choose car category (Mini ₹10/km → Luxury ₹30/km)
- **Step 3**: Select driver tier (Bronze/Silver/Gold/Platinum — multiplier from 1.0x to 1.08x)
- **Step 4**: Trip type selection (one-way vs round-trip)
- **Step 5**: Review fare breakdown and confirm
- Real-time fare calculation using the distance matrix + per-km pricing + driver multiplier + toll estimates + driver stay charges

### 3. Payment Page (`/payment`)
- Displays pending booking details
- **Fake Razorpay Modal**: Simulates Razorpay payment gateway UI (card/UPI/netbanking options)
- On "payment success": records payment, confirms booking, auto-assigns driver
- Generates a downloadable **Invoice** with all fare details

### 4. Login Page (`/login`)
- **Email/password login** with 2 demo accounts:
  - Customer: `demo@rajmarg.com` / `123456`
  - Admin: `admin@rajmarg.com` / `admin123`
- **OTP-based login**: Enter phone → receive fake OTP → login
- Premium dark UI with glassmorphism

### 5. Register Page (`/register`)
- New user registration form (name, email, password, phone)
- Stores user in Redux + localStorage

### 6. Customer Dashboard (`/dashboard`)
- View all past bookings (with status: pending/confirmed/completed/cancelled)
- Cancel pending bookings
- Rate completed rides (1-5 stars + comment)
- View payment history
- Account information display

### 7. Admin Panel (`/admin`)
- **Booking Management**: View all bookings, filter by status, update statuses
- **Fare Management**: Adjust per-km pricing for each car category in real-time
- **Driver Management**: View mock driver profiles, tiers, ratings
- **Revenue Dashboard**: Basic stats (total bookings, revenue, etc.)
- Reset prices to defaults

### 8. Live Tracking Page (`/live-tracking`)
- Simulated live ride tracking interface
- Shows driver info (name, photo, vehicle, phone)
- Animated ride status progression (Confirmed → On The Way → Arrived → Completed)
- No real GPS/map integration — purely UI simulation

### 9. Driver Portal (`/driver-portal`)
- **Driver login** with demo accounts (e.g., `driver@rajmarg.com` / `123456`)
- View assigned rides
- Accept/reject ride requests
- Update ride status (in progress → completed)
- View earnings and rating summary

---

## Business Logic

### Fare Calculation Formula
```
Total = (Distance × PerKmPrice × DriverMultiplier) + TollEstimate + DriverStayCharge
```

- **Distance**: Looked up from a hardcoded Gujarat distance matrix (70+ city pairs)
- **PerKm Price**: Varies by car category (₹10 to ₹30/km), admin-adjustable
- **Driver Multiplier**: Based on driver tier — Bronze (1.0x), Silver (1.03x), Gold (1.05x), Platinum (1.08x)
- **Toll Estimate**: Distance-based tiers (0-50km: ₹0, 50-150km: ₹80, 150-300km: ₹180, 300-500km: ₹320, 500+km: ₹450)
- **Driver Stay Charge**: ₹800 flat fee for round trips > 250km one-way

### Car Categories
| Category | Per Km | Seats | Features |
|---|---|---|---|
| Mini | ₹10 | 4 | AC, Budget-Friendly |
| Sedan | ₹14 | 4 | AC, Extra Legroom, Highway Ready |
| SUV | ₹18 | 6 | AC, Large Boot, Family-Friendly |
| Premium SUV | ₹22 | 6 | Leather Interior, Premium Sound |
| Luxury | ₹30 | 4 | Chauffeur, Refreshments, WiFi |

### Driver Tiers
| Tier | Multiplier | Requirements |
|---|---|---|
| Bronze | 1.0x | New verified drivers |
| Silver | 1.03x | 100+ rides, 4.5+ rating |
| Gold | 1.05x | 500+ rides, 4.7+ rating |
| Platinum | 1.08x | 1000+ rides, 4.9+ rating |

### Supported Cities (22)
Ahmedabad, Surat, Vadodara, Rajkot, Gandhinagar, Bhavnagar, Jamnagar, Junagadh, Dwarka, Somnath, Kutch (Bhuj), Anand, Nadiad, Morbi, Mehsana, Navsari, Valsad, Bharuch, Porbandar, Mount Abu, Statue of Unity, Mumbai

### Auto Ride Simulation
After payment, the system automatically:
1. Assigns a random available driver
2. After 5s → toast "Driver is on the way!"
3. After 10s → toast "Driver has arrived!"
4. After 15s → toast "Ride completed! Rate your experience."

---

## State Management (Redux Toolkit)

7 Redux slices all persisted to **localStorage**:

| Slice | Key State | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `auth` | user, isAuthenticated | Customer login/register/logout |
| `booking` | bookings[], currentBooking | Booking CRUD with status tracking |
| `fare` | prices{} | Admin-adjustable per-km prices per car |
| `payment` | payments[], pendingPayment | Payment records |
| `driver` | drivers[], currentDriver, assignedBookings | Driver profiles, auth, ride assignments |
| `notification` | toasts[] | Toast notification queue |
| `rating` | ratings[] | Driver rating submissions |

---

## Design System & Theme

### Color Palette
- **Cream/Light**: `#FAFAF7` (background), `#F0EDE6` (dark cream)
- **Saffron/Gold**: `#C9A84C`, `#D4AF37`, `#B8943F`, `#E8C547` (accent/brand)
- **Royal Navy/Charcoal**: `#0A1628`, `#0D1B2A`, `#0B1120` (dark backgrounds)
- **Slate**: `#94A3B8` (secondary text)

### Typography
- **Display**: Playfair Display (serif) — headings, hero text
- **Body**: Inter (sans-serif) — general text
- **Alternative**: DM Sans — loaded but used sparingly

### Design Features
- **Dark mode** toggle support (via class-based switching)
- **Glassmorphism** cards (`backdrop-blur`, semi-transparent backgrounds)
- **Gold glow effects** on cards and buttons
- **Gujarati cultural pattern** backgrounds (subtle radial gradients)
- **Framer Motion page transitions** (fade + slide)
- **Custom scrollbar** (gold-tinted thin scrollbar)
- **Floating gold particles** animation
- **Premium gradient buttons** (gold gradient with charcoal text)
- **PWA support** (installable, offline caching for fonts and images)

---

## Current Limitations / Areas for Improvement

1. **No real backend** — Everything is mock data + localStorage. No database, no real API calls.
2. **No real authentication** — Hardcoded demo accounts, no JWT/session management, no password hashing.
3. **No real payment gateway** — Fake Razorpay modal, no actual money processing.
4. **No real maps/GPS** — Static distance matrix instead of Google Maps API, no live location tracking.
5. **No real-time features** — No WebSocket/SSE for live updates between driver and customer.
6. **No route protection** — Any page is accessible without login (no auth guards on routes).
7. **Single booking page is just a wrapper** — Booking.jsx only renders BookingWizard, may need direct access to booking states.
8. **No search/filter on cities** — City selection is basic dropdown, no autocomplete.
9. **No booking history export** — No PDF/CSV download of past rides.
10. **No responsive testing evidence** — Responsive classes are used but thorough mobile testing may be needed.
11. **No error boundaries** — No React error boundary components for graceful error handling.
12. **No unit/integration tests** — No test files or testing framework configured.
13. **No i18n/localization** — Only English, no Gujarati or Hindi language support.
14. **Images from Unsplash/RandomUser** — Car images are Unsplash URLs, driver photos from randomuser.me (may break if services change).
15. **No SEO optimization** — Single `index.html`, no SSR/SSG for search engine crawling.

---

## How to Run

```bash
cd rajmarg-elite
npm install
npm run dev          # Starts Vite dev server (usually http://localhost:5173)
npm run build        # Production build to /dist
npm run preview      # Preview production build
```

